An elemental companion may be summoned (and unsummoned) by the character. An unsummoned companion can be recalled after a short cooldown time. If an elemental companion is killed, it cannot be summoned again until the character rests. At 1st level you summon a small elemental. At 4th level it grows into a medium elemental. At 10th level it grows into a large elemental. At 16th level it grows into a huge elemental. At 22nd level it grows into a greater elemental. At 28th level it grows into an elder elemental.